## 1) Import the file "BDD_VICAN.csv"

```{r}
data <- read.csv("BDD_VICAN.csv", sep = ";", dec = ",", encoding = "UTF-8")

names(data) = tolower(names(data)) # removing capital letters as working with them can be annoying
```

